race.description: Battery Wise Sunshine Coast Maiden Handicap
race.comment: BOSS MODE (6) resumes here but showed enough in his first preparation to suggest he can be competitive in a race of this calibre. Revved up for this with a recent trial placing and shapes as a key runner. SILVER SMASH (13) was thereabouts in both outings in her first campaign before being given time to mature. Expect a strong showing while fresh. BENT BRIDGE (5) strips fitter third-up from the spell and gets some weight relief with the 1.5kg claim. In the mix. EMPHATIQUE (12) was in the market when on debut and where there's smoke there's fire. Keep safe. INSAIN LADY (18) next in line from the low draw.
